structure.unit: LEVY AND ASSESSMENT OF PROPERTY TAXES

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 254, sec. 10. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4111.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Reports on spirits on which Federal tax has been paid or is due or removed for transfer out of state; payment of taxes due.
